title: DC Comics Audiobook Collection, Version 1 (14 books)
description:
Here is a compilation of a bunch of official and unofficial audiobooks for novels based on DC Comics. They are all in MP3 format. Here are the titles included:

-52 by Greg Cox
-The Adventures of Superman by George Lowther (fanmade audiobook)
-Batman: Dead White by John Shirley
-Batman: No Man's Land by Greg Rucka
-Countdown by Greg Cox
-Crisis on Infinite Earths by Marv Wolfman
-Infinite Crisis by Greg Cox
-It's Superman! by Tom De Haven
-Justice League of America: Batman: Stone King by Alan Grant
-Justice League of America: Exterminators by Christopher Golden
-Justice League of America: Green Lantern: Hero's Quest by Dennis O'Neil
-The Last Days of Krypton by Kevin J. Anderson
-Smallville: Arrival by Michael Teitelbaum (fanmade audiobook)
-Wayne of Gotham by Tracy Hickman

Plus the short story Smallville: Toy: Part 1 from Smallville Magazine #17.

More to come!
